To download and install app on Facebook, use "App Promotion" Ads in Faceboo Ads Manager.

Step-by-step:
1. Open Meta Ads Manager

    Go to Meta Ads Manager and click Create Campaign.

2. Choose Campaign Objective

    Select App Promotion (or “App Installs” in some accounts).

    This tells Meta to find people likely to install apps.

3. Select App

Choose:
    - Google Play for Android app
    - Apple App Store for iPhone app

Search the app by name or paste the app link.

    Example:
        https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.example.app

4. Set Conversion Location

    Choose where you want installs from:

    - App Store
    - Google Play
    - Direct app events (if SDK installed)

5. Set Audience

    Target by:
    - Country / City
    - Age
    - Gender
    - Interests
    - Device type (Android / iPhone)
    - WiFi only (optional)

    Example:
    - Country: USA
    - Age: 18–45
    - Interest: Online shopping / Gaming / Finance (depends on app)

6. Set Budget

    Start with:
    - $5–$20/day test budget per ad set

    After good results, increase slowly.

7. Placement

Use Advantage+ Placements (automatic)
    Ads show on:
    - Facebook Feed
    - Instagram Feed
    - Stories
    - Reels
    - Audience Network
    - Messenger

8. Create Ad Creative

    Use:
      ✅ App screenshot/video
      ✅ Demo video
      ✅ Attractive headline

    Example:

      Primary Text:
        “Download now and get 20% discount on your first order!”

      Headline:
      - Install Now

      CTA Button:
      - Install Now / Download

9. Add Tracking

Install:

Meta SDK or
Firebase + AppsFlyer / Adjust

This helps track:

installs
purchases
registrations
10. Publish & Monitor

Check metrics like:

CPI = Cost Per Install
CTR = Click Through Rate
CPC = Cost Per Click
ROAS if app sells products
Pro Tips:
Use video ads for better install rate.
Run separate campaigns for Android and iPhone.
Retarget people who clicked but didn’t install.
Create Lookalike Audience from existing users.

This is the best Facebook ad type for app downloads and installs.
